    "quiz_mode_title": "Pick right quiz mode",
    "quiz_mode_text": "Hitamo what this quiz is for. Exit Ticket suzumas uno musi’s learning. Pre-Suzuma probes prior koyawledge before teaching na surfaces gaps as concept cards na a one-kanda \"Explain ku ishuri\" AJetwebwe broadcast. Formative Suzuma is a quick mid-isomo pulse. Spaced Review tracks each umunegohure’s cross-igihe c'akazi retention na a per-concept sparkline. Each mode tunes prompts, item-ubwoko mix, na live dashboard latwebwetwebwet."
