    "concept_sort_game": "birikora concept sort game interface kuri categorization practice. Ktwebweka items into vyukuri category buckets ku demonstrate understanding of ishuriification concepts. Jetwebwemmediate feedinyuma erekanas vyukuri na invyukuri placements. Supports 2-4 categories na any igitigiri of sortable items. Vyiza cane kuri amajambo tiers, science ishuriifications, canke grammar sorting.",
